			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Wizard Guide</b></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><A href="mailto:Masta_P@worldnet.att.net">Cannabus</a> | 
		            9/2/1999 3:00:00 PM</b></font></p>
		         <a href="guides.asp">
		         <font face="verdana" size="2">Return to guide listing.</font></a>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Wizard guide<BR>
Spellin will be bad<BR>
<BR>
Ok I am a gnome wizard and  I Love it. There is nothing that satisfies me more that being 2 foot nuthin and being able to steal a kill from and ogre warrior. That is QUALITY.<BR>
<BR>
1st - 4th lvl<BR>
 	The first lvl for gnome wizard sux cause you have to learn time your casts. Ohh well&#8230; once you get to lvl two ask someone to take you to kelethin or tell you the way&#8230;I am not going to tell you, consider it a quest. Now head to the newbie ground being lvl 2 kill everything you see and save your mana for things that con even and kill the bluers with your dagger. Lvl 3 to four is hard stay at the newbie area and masacre everything and you will do so search out widow hatchlings and pawns. Once you hit four you will be happy &#8216;cause you get this amazing thing called meditate. This allows you to regen your mana faster and mem your spells twice as fast which is good cause wow its annoying to do that everytime you die.<BR>
<BR>
4th &#8211;7th <BR>
Head to the Orc hill and group with someone older than you to kill everything after you have bought shock of fire and root. After that you cast root once in a while and pump your training points into alteration.<BR>
At five you can solo orcs that con blue to you. Hit them with your dagger and cast your spell. You won&#8217;t loose exp when you die right now so it&#8217;s a good Idea to solo cause you will lvl quick. Ok 6 is the same thing kil everything that cons blue and then you hit  7 the slowest of lvls. Just keep up what you where doin and stick with it above all. <BR>
<BR>
8th!!!!!!!<BR>
         You&#8217;ve hit eight lvl now and personally I congradulate you. This is a hard part to get too.<BR>
Go to felwtih and purchase firebolt after saving ALL your money cause these spells are frikin expensive.<BR>
Ok now is where you lvl fast. Head to the chessboard by getting somone to toake you to the BB entrance on the path and then once you zone follow the wall to the right all the way down till ou see a big chesboard. Ak people if you can join and if you gwt one other who kills well you can sit back and cast your firebolt spell you will lvl in about 2 hours of play f you hutn constantly. Kep pthis same thing up until you hit 11 now you might have a lot of boine ships head to kaladim by heading down the path that leads from the bb greaterfaydark zone to the t junction and hang a right. Check your book and head to the pallys guild in kaladim and the ngive a guy in there I can&#8217;t remember which  your chips he will give you armo and weapons which you can sell for cash. After doin this you could buy lesser shielding or Ice shoc kwhich I recommend. At 11 head to the orc tower  (get directions)  and group for massive exp and rawhide armor which can be sold for up to 8 gold a piece. And 3 gold form some of the orcales loots.<BR>
<BR>
12th <BR>
        Head past kaladim ion the trail that goes by the tunnel into it and then  get on the boat and stay on it unitl you zone 2 times and it will say east freeport find your way to the magic place in north freeport and buy bind affinity and lightinign shock with nay money. Priority goes to lightnign shocl then bind affinity and then halo of lighti n the temple of marr. I choose to stay here and head strait out the gate into the east comons then head into the tunnel and then into Nro and folow the sand cliffs to the right of the tunnel till I hit oasis of marr where I curently am and half a bub from 13 On Povar server My Name Is Cannabus send a tell if you have read my guide!<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Fire, Ice, and Lightning Be,<BR>
Boon to wizards Gnome and Elfy,<BR>
Burn and slash everything you see<BR>
Crush the userpers whoever they BE!!!<BR>
<BR>
Cannabus&#8230;..<BR>
